h can be leveraged to better\ncombat future pandemics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 May 2020 21:59:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 May 2020 09:25:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 01:39:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-22"}
