ed under various settings using the\nproposed framework. More importantly, the distilled dataset has shown its\ncapabilities of boosting the performance of FER with negligible additional\ncomputational costs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 May 2020 09:36:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 13:07:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 Nov 2021 00:12:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 30 Nov 2021 06:28:08 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 9 Dec 2021 04:07:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-10"}
