ives, we also show that the averaging of cubic layers results in an\nequivalent medium with tetragonal (not cubic) symmetry. Additionally, we\npresent concise formulations of stability conditions for low symmetry classes,\nsuch as trigonal, orthotropic, and monoclinic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 May 2020 13:02:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Jan 2021 12:41:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-08"}
